インタフェースの使用
org.interledger.InterledgerPacket.VoidHandler

  • InterledgerPacket.VoidHandlerを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.interledger
    The main package for top-level Interledger objects.
    org.interledger.codecs
    This package holds all codecs for the Interledger project, including top-level interfaces and abstract classes that can be utilized to create more specific codecs, such as for ASN.1 OER, JSON, Protobuf, and more.

    • org.interledgerでのInterledgerPacket.VoidHandlerの使用

      InterledgerPacket.VoidHandlerを実装しているorg.interledgerのクラス 
      修飾子とタイプ クラスと説明
      static class  InterledgerPacket.VoidHandler.AbstractVoidHandler
      An abstract implementation of InterledgerPacket.VoidHandler for allowing callers to specify logic based upon an unknown result type extending InterledgerPacket.
      static class  InterledgerPacket.VoidHandler.AbstractVoidHandler.HelperHandler
      A utility class that provides default implementations of InterledgerPacket.VoidHandler.AbstractVoidHandler methods so that a caller is only forced to implement the handlers that are of interest.

    • org.interledger.codecsでのInterledgerPacket.VoidHandlerの使用

      InterledgerPacket.VoidHandler型のパラメータを持つorg.interledger.codecsのメソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      void CodecContext.readAndHandle(InputStream inputStream, InterledgerPacket.VoidHandler packetHandler)
      Read an object from the buffer according to the rules defined in the CodecContext, and handle any terminating logic inside of packetHandler.
